            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "If you want a multi source-file plugin you presently need to have the layout\n\n```\nrplugin/python3/myplugin.py  # empty\nrplugin/python3/myplugin/__init__.py # contains handlers\nrplugin/python3/myplugin/util1.py\nrplugin/python3/myplugin/util2.py # etc\n```\n\nbut I'm not sure if the empty `myplugin.py` is intrinsically necessary, it might be a side effect how `UpdateRemotePlugins` searches for plugins.\n(If you only want one file `rplugin/python3/myplugin.py` suffices)\n",
